Using ES6 Import/Export with Jest:

1. Install Babel:

npm install --save-dev babel-jest

2. Configure 'package.json':

{
	"scripts": {
		"test": "jest"
	},
	"jest": {
		"transform": {
			"^.+\\.jsx?$": "babel-jest"
		}
	}
}

3. Install Babel preset:

npm install @babel/preset-env --save-dev

4. Create '.babelrc' file:

{
	"presets": ["@babel/preset-env"]
}